  "title": "[사당동 이수 다이어트/사당동 한방다이어트]요요현상 줄여주는 한방다이어트",
  "addDate": "2013. 3. 25.",
  "categoryNo": "11",
  "parentCategoryNo": "11",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110164269877",
  "html_size": 186743,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110164269877\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110164269877\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'3028108_10';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<DIV class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>[사당동 이수 다이어트/사당동 한방다이어트]</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>요요현상 줄여주는 한방다이어트</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>처음 다이어트를 시작해서 감량에 성공은 했지만</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;유지가 안되여 요요현상이 일어 나는 경우가 많습니다</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>요요현상이 나타나지 않고 건강하게 감량할 수 있는 한방 다이어트 프로그램에</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>대해서 알려 드리겠습니다</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/cdd2aff355456318.png\" width=\"498\" height=\"339\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 498px; rheight: 339px\" id=\"20130325_118/isuhani_1364177375979bYD61_PNG/%C3%BB%B9%CC%B7%A1%C8%AF1.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A64D5B35')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/cdd2aff355456318.png\"></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>살이 찐다는 것은 단순한 체중 증가의 문제가 아니라 체지방이 몸속에 과잉</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>축척된 상태이므로 체지방을 줄이는 것이 무엇보다 중요하며 보기에는 날씬 하지만</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>근육이 적고 체지방이 많은 마른 비만이신 분들도 다이어트가 필요합니다</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130325_201/isuhani_1364175662668GQTMs_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2_%C7%C1%B7%CE%B1%D7%B7%A5%C0%E5%C1%A1%BA%F1%B8%B8%BA%F1%B8%B8%B0%A8%B7%AE22.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"481\" height=\"187\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 481px; rheight: 187px\" id=\"20130325_201/isuhani_1364175662668GQTMs_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2_%C7%C1%B7%CE%B1%D7%B7%A5%C0%E5%C1%A1%BA%F1%B8%B8%BA%F1%B8%B8%B0%A8%B7%AE22.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A64D5B35')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130325_201/isuhani_1364175662668GQTMs_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2_%C7%C1%B7%CE%B1%D7%B7%A5%C0%E5%C1%A1%BA%F1%B8%B8%BA%F1%B8%B8%B0%A8%B7%AE22.jpg?type=w3\"></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>이수 한방다이어트 프로그램의 장점은 체중 감량 뿐 아니라 체내 독소(어혈) 배출을 하게 하고</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>개인의 체질에 맞는 맞춤형 다이어트를 통해 체지방 감소 뿐 아니라 체질개선까지 생각하여</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>감량하는 건강한 한방 다이어트법 입니다</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0522691033b08fec.png\" width=\"550\" height=\"319\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 554px; rheight: 322px\" id=\"20130325_273/isuhani_1364175744013izRTj_PNG/%BA%F1%B8%B8%B0%A8%B7%AE1.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A64D5B35')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0522691033b08fec.png\"></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>이수 한방 다이어트 프로그램으로 감량에 성공하신 분에 기록입니다</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>식이요법/운동요법/체형관리 를 통해서 체중조절로 2개월에 8kg감량에 성공하셨고</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>요요현상이 나타나지 않게 꾸준히 관리 하셨습니다</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<DIV align=center><div>\n<iframe src=\"https://mashup.map.naver.com/view.nhn?mid=bl012984104%40s13104608&type=total\" width=\"402\" height=\"352\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" onerror=\"return true;\" onabort=\"return true;\" style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:8px;background-color:white;\" title=\"포스트에 첨부된 지도\"></iframe>\n</div></DIV>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=left>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=left>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<STRONG><SPAN style=\"COLOR: #00b0a2\"> 이수한의원 진료안내</SPAN></STRONG></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/395f32dd7ba53a59.png\" width=\"547\" height=\"172\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 547px; rheight: 172px\" id=\"20130325_56/isuhani_1364177999084RPyyw_PNG/%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8%C1%F8%B7%E1%BD%C3%B0%A3%C7%A52.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A64D5B35')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/395f32dd7ba53a59.png\"></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><pzp-pc-layout class=\"_naverVideo _vnl\" vid=\"E678A843E8D3D991F75920B7933A170CBA14\" key=\"V122110c4332d1ea596fbfd4896a44ac143e606d3570ab161b03f7d34c876ce871b7efd4896a44ac143e6\" outKeyMode=\"false\" hasLink=\"true\" logNo=\"110164269877\" domain-or-blogId=\"isuhani\" style=\"width:512px; height:321px;\">\n  <pzp-pc-header class=\"pzp-pc__header\">\n    <pzp-pc-content-info class=\"pzp-pc__content-info\">\n      <pzp-pc-content-title></pzp-pc-content-title>\n      <pzp-pc-play-count></pzp-pc-play-count>\n    </pzp-pc-content-info>\n    <pzp-pc-toolbar class=\"pzp-pc__toolbar\">\n        <pzp-pc-share-button class=\"pzp-pc__share-button\" data-style=\"type_player\" data-player-target-id=\"spi_player_E678A843E8D3D991F75920B7933A170CBA14\"></pzp-pc-share-button>\n    </pzp-pc-toolbar>\n  </pzp-pc-header>\n<span id=\"spi_player_E678A843E8D3D991F75920B7933A170CBA14\" class=\"pzp-pc__social-plugin-container\"></span>\n</pzp-pc-layout>\n \r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bace2a09d330ed1d.png\" width=\"266\" height=\"66\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 266px; rheight: 66px\" id=\"20130325_267/isuhani_1364178118371qcsdc_PNG/2013-03-18_14%3B49%3B33.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A64D5B35')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bace2a09d330ed1d.png\"></P></DIV></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
